INSERT INTO usage_tracking (user_id, resource_type, usage_count, period_start, period_end)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
            ON CONFLICT (user_id, resource_type, period_start)
            DO UPDATE SET 
                usage_count = usage_tracking.usage_count + $3,
                updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
